   3:../application/src/main.c ****   * @file    main.c
   4:../application/src/main.c ****   * @brief   Application main program for STM32F401
   5:../application/src/main.c ****   * @details This application demonstrates a simple LED blink at a slower rate
   6:../application/src/main.c ****   *          than the bootloader to visually indicate that the application is running.
